'''Samba Félix N'diaye''' (6 Werurwe 1945–6 Ugushyingo 2009), yari umukinnyi wa [[Senegali|firime]] wa Sénégalese.  Imwe mu nkingi za mbere mu nganda za sinema zo muri [[Senegali]], Ndiaye afatwa nka se wa documentaire nyafurika<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=3344</ref>. Yakoze  Documentaire zamamaye cyane ''Trésors des poubelles'', ''Ngor, l'esprit des lieux'', ''Les malles'' na ''Geti Tey'' .  Usibye icyerekezo, ni umwanditsi akaba n'umukinnyi wa sinema<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/felix-samba-ndiaye/</ref>.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Ndiaye yavutse ku ya 6 Werurwe 1945 i Dakar, muri [[Senegali]]<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/45827_1</ref>.  Yahoraga yitabira club ya firime yikigo ndangamuco cyabafaransa i Dakar yabikoraga akamenyero. Nyuma yaje kwiga amategeko nubukungu muri kaminuza ya Dakar<ref>https://iffr.com/en/persons/samba-f%C3%A9lix-ndiaye</ref> . Nyuma yize muri kaminuza ya Paris VIII ahabwa Masters muri Sinema na Audiovisual Studies. Hanyuma yifatanije na Institut Lumière kwiga cinematografi no gutunganya<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/samba-felix-ndiaye/3344</ref>. Yapfuye ku ya 6 Ugushyingo 2009 i Dakar afite imyaka 64 azize ibibazo bya malariya yo mu bwonko . Nyuma yaje gushyingurwa mu irimbi rya Yoff<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/1240_1</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1974, yayoboye documentaire ye ya mbere ''yitwa Perantal'', mu rwego rwo kubona impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri sinema<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/samba-felix-ndiaye/3344</ref>. Mu 1978, yakoze ''Geti Tey'' ngufi yaganiriye ku ngorane abarobyi b'abanyabukorikori bahuye na Kayar, Hann cyangwa Soumbédioune ibikorwa byabo bibangamiwe n'uburobyi. Nyuma yibyo, Ndiaye yakoze urukurikirane rwa firime eshanu ngufi ziteranijwe ku mutwe wa ''Trésors des poubelles'' mu 1989. Muri uwo mwaka, yakoze ''Aqua'' ngufi, "metonymy yo mumijyi" itagira amagambo.<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/9465_1</ref>  

Mu 1994, Ndiaye yakoze filime ye ya mbere ya ''Ngor, l'esprit des lieux'' ivuga ku baturage ba Ngor, umudugudu uherereye mu nkengero za Dakar<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=3344</ref>. Kuva mu mpera za 1990, ahanini yari ahangayikishijwe na documentaire zishingiye kuri politiki maze akora ''Lettre à Senghor'' mu 1998.  Nkumwanditsi, yanditse documentaire yu ''[[Rwanda]], pour mémoire'' yibanze kuri jenoside yo mu [[Rwanda]] yo mu 1994. Muri 2007 mumyaka ye ya nyuma, Ndiaye yakoze documentaire ''Ibibazo à la terre natale'' .  Muri 2012, yatsindiye igihembo mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cordoba kubera filime ye ''Trésors des poubelles'' .<ref>https://karoninka.com/project/examen-detat/</ref>

